Michael P. Gianoni 
Executive Compensation
As President and CEO at BLACKBAUD INC, Michael P. Gianoni  made $5,709,266 in total compensation.  Of this total $679,526 was received as a salary, $658,436 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $4,279,804 was awarded as stock and $91,500 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


