Insider Activity


Individual




Michael P. Gianoni



Mr. Michael P. Gianoni is on the Board of Directors at Teradata Corp. and Blackbaud, Inc. Mr. Gianoni was previously employed as Executive Vice President & General Manager by CheckFree Corp., EVP & Group President-Financial Institutions by Fiserv, Inc., Executive Vice President & General Manager by CheckFree Investment Services, Senior Vice President-eSolutions Division by DST Systems, Inc., a Principal by CANBERRA Industries, Inc., a Principal by Objective Data Storage LLC, a Principal by Sequent Computer Systems, Inc., and a Principal by Wang Laboratories, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Charter Oak State College and an MBA from the University of New Haven.



